{"tid":1464126,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「文宣急進」 － 下一波靠依樣！！！","createTime":"2019-08-13T14:27:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T15:18:35.000Z","uid":268388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"47865b7a213f5ca1718dcf7d17b10bae4051bcc4","tid":1464126,"uid":268388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:27:19.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">話說屋企人<span style=\"color: blue;\">不是藍</span>，直情<span style=\"color: red;\">係「紅」</span>。好多大陸親戚依幾日都打黎問香港咩事，香港點！！<br />\n咁你地知啦，藍都重有得兜下，紅的話直情不停輸出錯誤資訊，包括同大陸親戚講係學生收左外國人錢＆佢地打警察＆佢地掉國旗等等。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">文宣有樣野可以做：<br />\n1.好簡易咁講下到底<span style=\"color: red;\">咩係逃犯條例</span>（佢地大陸咩7都唔識，連咩事都唔知）<br />\n2.講下香港學生做緊咩<br />\n3.話俾佢地知，佢地收到咩資訊（cctv大陸俾咩佢地睇）vs 香港有咩俾到佢地睇（香港實際係點），令佢地知，到底大陸遮蓋左咩唔俾佢地知，而現實係點！！！<br />\n4.講下點解學生會用命去抵抗黑警（用圖／文字話佢地知黑警對學生做左咩）<br />\n5.再講下大陸司法有幾咁離地，所以學生先咁抗拒大陸司法（山西租屋事件可煲大佢）<br />\n</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">動之以情，說之以理</div></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"d4ac80cac5070692363f4fa8f910d3c9e7796da6","tid":1464126,"uid":268388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:27:34.000Z","msg":"文宣急進"},{"pid":"66eece9d092a8b9f69dade8adb160bea2b163d99","tid":1464126,"uid":268388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:27:44.000Z","msg":"文宣急進"},{"pid":"ff3edab3c4bcb0cddd14feae7ce314e6ca771f0d","tid":1464126,"uid":268388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:27:57.000Z","msg":"文宣急進"},{"pid":"08e66d8b00dbdeb09e89cd31c9944959d5e20b44","tid":1464126,"uid":268388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:28:26.000Z","msg":"文宣急進"},{"pid":"52d0b7b43a601f22f788877566429916c6139698","tid":1464126,"uid":268388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019